headline: Duke Energy to sell Piedmont Natural Gas Tennessee business for $2.48 billion
summary: Duke Energy said it would sell its Tennessee natural gas distribution business to Spire for $2.48 billion in cash.

headline: Spire to acquire Duke Energy’s Piedmont Natural Gas business in Tennessee, US
summary: The acquisition, pending regulatory approvals, will result in the creation of a new business unit, Spire Tennessee.
